info: Rating, 4 stars,  · December 2023,  · Stayed over a week
rating_comment: Great place to stay, decent neighbourhood. Very responsive and helpful host. as for the room itself, it was great. nicely furnished, has pretty much everything you need. apart from a couple of cobwebs and the smell of varnish from the new wooden paneling/closets. everything was absolutely fantastic.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · November 2023,  · Stayed with kids

rating_comment: The place was a great place but we did come across a bit of hiccups. I loved the communications that Minhazul had and professionalism as well. As for the hiccups it is Bangladesh so it was expected. Only thing that we did have a slight issue with was when we checked in, the place was not cleaned properly (kitchen and bathroom) as there were dusts and hair all over. But upon request, Minhazul sent the cleaning staff to re'clean per our liking. We also extended our stay for another 10 days without an issue. Thank Minhazul and Alamin!
